{"tid":1586481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過黑警可以將陣亡義士用高鐵運走？","createTime":"2019-09-22T03:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:02:17.000Z","uid":36058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"feb0e1a179758d5f45a6f301ed1bfd22b83c9cc3","tid":1586481,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"而家咁嘅局勢，有理由相信黑警已經係北京直接操控，當中混入左好多解放軍同武警，如果佢哋殺咗人，一定要想盡辦法隱瞞，否則，一上法庭，北京就等於出動左解放軍，令人聯想到天安門事件，北京承受唔到呢一個政治風險，所以必定會事急馬行田，將義士直接用高鐵送走，然後响香港剷除所有證據。當中亦唔牽涉到前線警員，佢哋冇可能會知道，因為怕洩漏風聲，所以全部都係武警或解放軍一手包辦。當然，黑警高層係知道呢件事。"},{"pid":"f724425b3cc55312640e53a38ab59440911e46d8","tid":1586481,"uid":128569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T03:39:52.000Z","msg":"其實美國都開到聲話死左人 點會無可能"},{"pid":"e9d801a944d2fe03385de2ff74dd5281b25982e9","tid":1586481,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"009616ad12296f237e17ea6a6ea0d57e2b154e58","tid":1586481,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d801a944d2fe03385de2ff74dd5281b25982e9","tid":1586481,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f724425b3cc55312640e53a38ab59440911e46d8","tid":1586481,"uid":128569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T03:39:52.000Z","msg":"其實美國都開到聲話死左人 點會無可能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"之前有po 開過"},{"pid":"abaf7b27713f38ed79b19028b9d775a663fbacb5","tid":1586481,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"解放軍醫院有殮房"},{"pid":"2d2f1c757074ae8dc57af1928192ddad01add264","tid":1586481,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"一定要查明真相，要港鐵交出CCTV"},{"pid":"92ccf52b4a80d2eae61514256edd79b0a72c0309","tid":1586481,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:02:17.00